        "Details": "Originally developed by the first Star League, the Tolson was designed to serve as the ultimate command and control and electronic warfare platform of its era. The original designer, Dr. Transient, elected to give it a sleek appearance to help it better resist enemy sensors and equipped it with the best technology the Star League could muster. The Tolson is built on a 300-rated XL Engine and clad in 10 tons of Ferro-Fibrous armor. For weaponry it carries two Large Lasers and a LRM-10 but the real prize of the mech is the in-built Command Console as well as the Beagle Active Probe, Guardian ECM, Narc Launcher, and TAG system, all of which give it unparalleled battlefield control.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
